[dataminr_api://<name>]
dataminr_account = Dataminr account to fetch data from
alert_type = Select Alert Type(s) to collect.
lists_names = Select Lists Names from which to collect Alerts.

[dataminr_api_v4://<name>]
dataminr_account = Dataminr account to fetch data from
alert_type = Select Alert Type(s) to collect.
lists_names = Select Lists Names from which to collect Alerts.

[dataminr_webhook://<name>]
dataminr_account = Dataminr account to fetch data from
alert_type = Select Alert Type(s) to collect.
lists_names = Select Lists Names from which to collect Alerts.
hec_token = Splunk HEC token to use for receiving data from Dataminr Pulse
dataminr_webhook_id = Dataminr webhook Id